reviewText: Great music from one of my all time favorites.
F & S classics from their tv shows

Flatt & Scruggs pretty much "wrote the book" for first class professionalism, as well as first class Bluegrass music. These videos may be over 50 years old, but are solid testimony that Lester & Earl have NEVER been surpassed--even by today's standards.

This was a gift that was Very much appreciated. Excellent quality video and audio, and I love the old commercials they did in the show as well as the music.  I hope to pick up more from this series soon.

Another 5 star stellar performance from Lester and Earl and The Foggy Mountain Boys.  I remember as a kid how excited I would be when Lester and Earl were guests on The Beverly Hillbillies Show.  These well preserved vintage tv shows are a real treat not to be missed for the Flatt & Scruggs fan.  If you are not a fan, you will be after you view these DVD's.  Thanks to all who made these wonderful shows available.  They are classics!  I am already looking forward to the release of volume 6 & 7.
Very nice to see the old country music shows available. Hope they continue with lots more of Flatt & Scruggs!!!
